</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">Solution</span> <span class="o">{</span>
    <span class="n">fun</span> <span class="nf">solution</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nl">n:</span> <span class="nc">Long</span><span class="o">):</span> <span class="nc">Long</span> <span class="o">{</span>
        <span class="n">val</span> <span class="n">sqrt</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nc">Math</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">sqrt</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">toDouble</span><span class="o">())</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="nf">if</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">sqrt</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="mf">1.0</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mf">0.0</span><span class="o">)</span> <span class="o">{</span>
            <span class="nc">Math</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">pow</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">sqrt</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">,</span> <span class="mf">2.0</span><span class="o">).</span><span class="na">toLong</span><span class="o">()</span>
        <span class="o">}</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="o">{</span>
            <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1L</span>
        <span class="o">}</span>
    <span class="o">}</span>
<span class="o">}</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<div class="card h-100 my-u-padding"><div class="insertcover"><a target="_blank" class="text-dark" href="https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/12935"><div class=""><img class="inserturl" src="/assets/images/study/programmers.png" alt="programmers.co.kr" /></div><div class="insert-img-body"><h4 class="insert-img-title">연습문제 : 제일 작은 수 제거하기</h4><p class="insert-img-description">programmers.co.kr</p></div></a></div></div>

<p>작은수를 찾고, 해당 index를 알아서 빼줘야하는 고민을 하고 있엇는데, filter기능을 이해하면 한번에 해결이 가능하다.</p>

<div class="language-java highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
2
3
4
5
6
</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">Solution</span> <span class="o">{</span>
    <span class="n">fun</span> <span class="nf">solution</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nl">arr:</span> <span class="nc">IntArray</span><span class="o">):</span> <span class="nc">IntArray</span> <span class="o">{</span>
        <span class="k">if</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">arr</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">size</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">)</span> <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">intArrayOf</span><span class="o">(-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">)</span>
        <span class="k">else</span> <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">arr</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">filter</span><span class="o">{</span> <span class="n">it</span> <span class="o">!=</span> <span class="n">arr</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">min</span><span class="o">()</span> <span class="o">}.</span><span class="na">toIntArray</span><span class="o">()</span>
    <span class="o">}</span>
<span class="o">}</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<div class="card h-100 my-u-padding"><div class="insertcover"><a target="_blank" class="text-dark" href="https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/12937"><div class=""><img class="inserturl" src="/assets/images/study/programmers.png" alt="programmers.co.kr" /></div><div class="insert-img-body"><h4 class="insert-img-title">연습문제 : 짝수와 홀수</h4><p class="insert-img-description">programmers.co.kr</p></div></a></div></div>

<p>전형적인 문제풀이</p>

<div class="language-java highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
2
3
</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">Solution</span> <span class="o">{</span>
    <span class="n">fun</span> <span class="nf">solution</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nl">num:</span> <span class="nc">Int</span><span class="o">)</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="k">if</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">num</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="o">)</span> <span class="s">"Even"</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="s">"Odd"</span>
<span class="o">}</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<p>and operator를 사용하여 해결한다. 여기서 and는 논리연산 and를 의미하며 비트연산으로 판단한다.</p>

<div class="language-java highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
2
3
</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="kd">class</span> <span class="nc">Solution</span> <span class="o">{</span>
    <span class="n">fun</span> <span class="nf">solution</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nl">num:</span> <span class="nc">Int</span><span class="o">):</span> <span class="nc">String</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="k">if</span> <span class="o">(</span><span class="n">num</span> <span class="n">and</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">)</span> <span class="s">"Odd"</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="s">"Even"</span>
<span class="o">}</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

